div.div:
Initialize project structure with core components for beatgoods idea voting platform
- Set up frontend with React, Vite, and TypeScript - Create backend server with Express and CSV data storage - Add Python CLI and web interface modules - Configure development tools and project dependencies - Implement basic idea voting functionality - Add logging, testing, and configuration files

Enhance SiteDumper crawler with advanced content saving and reporting features
- Implemented robust `save_content` method with multi-format export support - Added comprehensive `convert_to_markdown` method for detailed content conversion - Developed `generate_interim_report` and `generate_final_report` methods for detailed crawling insights - Improved error handling and logging during content saving process - Added support for compressing output files - Enhanced progress tracking with memory usage visualization
Created new branch main in wyattowalsh/open-webui-resources
